Introduction

NEWBEAT, formerly known as HinLOVE and HIGH&LOW, is a seven-member boy group under Beat Interactive. They made their debut on March 24, 2025, with the full-length album Raw and Rad.

The lineup consists of former Boys Planet contestant Minseok, Minsung, former TO1 member Yeojeong, Seohyun, Taeyang, Yunhu, and Riwoo.
